quran[431]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Mukama Katonda nanyini buyinza bwonna musukkulumu, era nga muyinza w'abuli kintu"
  67,2,"Oyo eyatonda okufa n'obulamu, olwokubageseza alabe ani asinga okukola obulungi. Naye ye Nnantakubwa ku mukono omusonyiyi"
  67,3,"Oyo eyatonda eggulu omusanvu nga myaliro, toyinza kulaba mu kutonda kwa Katonda kamogo konna w'etegereze abaffe olabamu obukyamu bwonna"
  67,4,Era zzaayo amaaso emirundi nemirundi eriiso lijja ku kuddira nga likooye era nga tolina kyofunyeeyo
  67,5,"Mazima eggulu eriri okumpi n'ensi twalinyiriza nemunyeeye ezaaka, era nga bitawuliro ebigoba Sitani era Sitani ezo twazitegekera ebibonerezo byomuliro Ssair"
  67,6,Ate bbo abaawakanya Katonda waabwe twabategekera ebibonerezo byamuliro Jahannama era buliba buddo bubi
  67,7,Bwe baligusuulwamu bagenda kuguwulira nga gutokota era nga gufuuwa
  67,8,Nga gubula kuyulikamu buli lwegunasulwangamu ekibinja abakuumi bagwo banababuuzanga nti temwajjirwa muntu yenna abatiisa (muliro guno)
  67,9,"Baliddamu nti weewawo omutiisa yatujjira naye netumulimbisa era netumugamba nti Katonda tassanga bubaka bwonna, ebyo byemulimu bubuze obuyitirivu"
  67,10,Baligamba nti singa twali tuwulira oba nga tutegeera (ebyatugambwanga) tetwandibadde bamu kwabo abayingira omuliro
  67,11,Nebeekakasaako ekyonoono kyabwe okufaafaganirwa kuli ku bantu bo mu muliro
  67,12,"Mazima abo abatya Katonda wabwe awamu n'okuba nga talabika, bagenda okufuna ekisonyiwo n'empeera ensuffu"
  67,13,Kyekimu mukwese ebigambo byamwe oba mubyatudde mazima yye amanyi ebiri mu bifuba
  67,14,Abaffe eyatonda ayinza obutamanya nga ate ye muyitirivu w'okumanya era nga mukugu nnyo
  67,15,"Yye yoyo eyabafuulira ensi enyangu, kale mutambule mu bitundu byayo mulye mu bigabwabye era gyali gye mugenda okudda"
  67,16,Musuubidde okuwona oyo ali waggulu ensi n'etabamira singa eba etabanguse
  67,17,"Oba musuubidde okuwona oyo ali waggulu n'atabasindikira muyaga, wabula mugenda kumanya okulabula kwange nga bwekwali okukulu"
  67,18,"Abo abaaliwo oluberyeberye lwabwe baalimbisa, naye tewamanya kyennabatusaako"
  67,19,"Abaffe tebalaba ebinyonyi ebibuukira waggulu wabwe nga byanjuluza ebiwawaatiro ate nga n'oluusi biwumbako, tewali kibikuumira mu bbanga okugyako Katonda omusaasizi, mazima ye alaba buli kintu"
  67,20,"Oba ani oyo asobola okubalwanirira n'abataasa atali Katonda, abawakanyi tebalina kyebaliko okugyako mawaggali"
  67,21,Ye abaffe ani oyo ayinza okubagabirira singa Katonda abajjako okugabirirakwe. Wabula baagwa mu kateebe k'okuwalaaza empaka n'okwewaggula
  67,22,Ye abaffe oyo atambula abwamiridde ku kyenyikye y'abeera kubulungamu oba oyo atambula nga yeegolodde ngali ku Kkubo eggolokofu
  67,23,Bagambe nti Katonda y'eyabatandikawo n'abassako amatu n'amaaso n'abawa n'emitima wabula mwebaza kitono
  67,24,Bagambe nti Katonda yoyo eyabassa mu nsi era nga mugenda kuzuukizibwa mudde gyali
  67,25,Bagamba mu kubalaata nti ebyo byemutulaganyisa biribaawo ddi bwe mubanga byemwogera bituufu
  67,26,"Bagambe nti okumanya okujjuvu okukwata ku nsonga eyo kuli wa Katonda, naye nze ndi mutiisa owolwatu"
  67,27,"Bwe baliraba e bibonerezo nga bisembedde, ebyenyi byabo abakafuwala bigenda kwekaba, awo balyoke bategezebwe nti ekyo nno kye mwagambanga nti kirituukaddi"
  67,28,"Bagambe nti, mulaba mutya singa Katonda anzikiriza n'abo abali nange oba n'atusaasira anti obuyinza bwonna buli gyali, naye ani alitaasa abakafiiri ku bibonerezo ebiruma"
  67,29,Bagambe nti yye Katonda omusaasizi gwetukkiriza era yekka gwetwesiga wabula lumu mulimanya ani ali mu bubuze obweyolefu
  67,30,Bagambe nti mulaba mutya singa amazzi gammwe bukya nga gakalidde ani ayinza okubawa amazzi agakulukuta amayonjo
  68,1,"Nuni, yemu kunyukuta ezikola walifu empalabu. Ndayidde e kalamu nebyebagiwandiisa"
  68,2,Mazima Gwe Muhammad ekyengera kyobwa Nabbi Katonda wo kyeyakuwa tekiyinza ku kufuula mulalu
  68,3,Era ddala oteekwa okufuna empeera etakutukawo
  68,4,Era mazima ddala Ggwe oli wampisa nungi nnyo
  68,5,Ojja kulaba nga nabo bwebagenda okulaba
  68,6,Ani kumwenna eyatukwako ekizibu kyeddalu
  68,7,Mazima Katondawo amanyidde ddala ani eyabula okuva ku kkubolye era nga bwamanyidde ddala abalungamu
  68,8,Kale nno togondera abo abalimbisa
  68,9,Bandyagadde nti singa obagondera nabo nebakugondera
  68,10,Era togeza n'ogondera buli alayiralayira ataliimu nsa
  68,11,Omugeyi atambuza olugambo
  68,12,"Omukodo, omulumbaganyi omwononefu"
  68,13,Mubi nnyo ate awamu n'ekyo mwana w'abwenzi
  68,14,Tomugondera olwokuba alina emmali n'abaana
  68,15,Omuntu oyo bwasomerwa ebigambo byaffe agamba nti nfumo z'abantu abedda
  68,16,Kulunaku lw’enkomerero tugenda kussa kunyindo ye akabonero akamulamba nga tanayingizibwa muliro
  68,17,"Mazima ffe twagezesa abantu be Makkah bwetwabaleetera enjala nga bwetwagezesa abantu abaalina enimiro yaabwe abalayira nti baali bagenda kukungula kumakya nnyo, olwo nno baleme kugabirako bantu balala"
  68,18,Wabula beerabira okugamba nti Insh'allah
  68,19,Katonda n'agisindikira nabbambula w'omuliro ogwa gizikiriza ekiro nga beebase
  68,20,Okugenda okukya ngankalu nga enkungule
  68,21,Ku lunaku olulaganye baakeera nnyo era nga buli omu agenda atemya kumunne
  68,22,Ngabagamba nti muzuukuke mugende mu nimiro yammwe bwe muba ddala nga munakungula nga bwemwagambye
  68,23,Baatambula nga bogera bwama
  68,24,Nga bwebagamba nti tebagenda kukkiriza Masikiini yenna kuyingira mu ssamba yaabwe
  68,25,Baatambula kumakya okwo nga bakakasa nti bagenda kutuukiriza kyebaali basazeewo eggulo limu
  68,26,Bwebaalaba ennimiro yaabwe b'agamba nti tubuze
  68,27,Sinakindi Katonda yagizikirizza olwe kigendererwa kyaffe ekibi ekyobutakkiriza kugabirako ba Masikiini
  68,28,"Eyali abasingako eddiini n'obuntu bulamu nabagamba nti ssabagambye nti obutawaako banaku buba bulyazamanyi bwennyini, era kati kyetuteekwa okukola kwekutendereza Katonda kuba tetunamanya yatusonyiye oba nedda"
  68,29,Olwo nno nebagamba nti yayawukana Katonda waffe mazima twabadde tweyisizza bubi
  68,30,Awamu nekyo baatandika okuwaanyisiganya ebigambo nga abamu banenya bannabwe
  68,31,Nebagamba nti mazima ffe tubadde bajeemu
  68,32,"Tusaba Katonda waffe emmali yaffe etokomose atuwanyisizeemu ebirungi, mazima ddala ew'a Katonda waffe yokka gyetusaba obuyambi"
  68,33,Bwebityo nno ebibonerezo bwebiba naye wabula ebibonerezo by'olunaku lw’enkomerero byebisinga obukakali singa baba ddala nga bamanyi
  68,34,Mazima abatya Katonda baategekerwa e jjana ez'ebyengera ewa Katonda waabwe
  68,35,Gwe ate abakkiriza twalibayisizza nga abonoonyi
  68,36,"Mwaba ki, e nsonga muzisalawo mutya"
  68,37,Simanyi mulinayo ekitabo mwemubisoma
  68,38,Era nga mukitaba ekyo mulimu nti mwe mulyesalirawo kyemwagala ku lunaku lw'enkomerero
  68,39,Oba mulina e ndagano gye twabawa nga etuukira ddala ku lunaku lw'enkomerero ngebawa ebbeetu okwesalirawo nga bwemulaba
  68,40,Babuuze ani eyesowolayo abe nga akulembera endowooza eyo
  68,41,"Oba balinayo (ababeesiguza) nga babayita babeezi ba Katonda, kale nno bajjanga nabo bwebaba nga bogera mazima"
  68,42,Ku lunaku olulibeera olw'okubikkula ku ntumbwe. Balikowoolwa okuvunnamira Katonda naye nga tebasobola
  68,43,"Nga amaaso gaabwe makakkamu olw'obuswavu, nga bajjudde okunyomebwa so nga ate baakowolwa okuvunnamira Katonda nga bakyali balamu ne batakikola"
  68,44,Kale ndeka noyo alimbisa ebigambo bino tujja kubatwaliriza mpola mpola nga tebamanyi
  68,45,"Era mbalindiriza, anti entegeka zange nnywevu"
  68,46,Abaffe wali obasabye empeera nebakaluubirirwa kusasula
  68,47,"Oba bamanyi ebyewala nga babiwandiika (nga bebyelamuza, era nga biraga nti bagenda kubeera bulungi)"
  68,48,"Kale nno beera mugumikiriza ku kusalawo kwa Katondawo, tobeera nga ow'ekyennyanja (Nabbi Yunus) eyatuuka okukowoola (Katondawe okumutaasa) nga ajjudde obunyiikaavu"
  68,49,Singa teyafuna kyengera ekyava ewa Katondawe (ekyokukiriza okwenenyakwe) yandikasukiddwa mu nsi e nkalu (etariiko bulamu) nga naye anenyezebwa
  68,50,Wabula Katonda yamulekera obwa Nabbi era namuteeka mu bantu abalongofu
  68,51,Abakafiiri basemberera ddala okukuzikiriza n'amaaso gaabwe amabi (olw'ekkonda eriri ku myoyo gyabwe) bwe bawulira Kur'ani era ne bagamba nti mazima yye (Nabbi) mulalu
  68,52,So ng'ate (Kur'ani) teri okugyako kya kujjukiza eri e bitonde
  69,1,Olunaku olwokwolesa amazima (olunaku lw’enkomerero)
  69,2,Olunaku lwokwolesa amazima kyeki
  69,3,Naye omanyi olunaku olwokwolesa amazima kyeki
  69,4,Abantu ba Thamud n'aba A'adi baalimbisa olunaku olwentiisa
  69,5,Abantu ba Thamud bazikirizibwa nakubwatuka okwamanyi
  69,6,Ate ba A'adi nebazikirizibwa nakibuyaga owamanyi ennyo eyalimu obunyogovu
  69,7,"Gweyabamazaamu ebiro musanvu nenaku munaana awatali kuyimiriramu, walaba abantu nga bagudde eri nga balinga enduli zemitende ezikutuddwako amasanso"
  69,8,Gwe mu kulaba waliwo eyawona
  69,9,"Farawo, n'abamukulembera, naabo abali kubyalo bya Luutu bayonoona"
  69,10,Ekyatuusa buli bamu okujeemera omubaka Katonda gwe yabatumira. Katonda kye yava abakwata olukwata oluyitirivu
  69,11,Aba Nuhu amazzi bwegaabooga okubawonya twabasaabaliza mulyato
  69,12,Olwo nno tulyoke tukibafuulire mmwe ekyokwebuulirira era gakitegeere amatu agategeera
  69,13,Naye engombe bwerifuyibwa olufuuwa olusooka
  69,14,Ensi nensozi birisitulwa nebimementulwa omulundi gumu
  69,15,Olwo nno olunaku lw’enkomerero luliba lutuuse
  69,16,"Eggulu ligenda kweyasaamu, nga ku lunaku olwo ligenda kuba lyabirivu"
  69,17,"Nga ba Malayika bali kumabbali galyo, nga waggulu waabwe kulunaku olwo ba Malayika munaana beebalisitula Arishi y'amukama Katonda wo"
  69,18,Ku lunaku olwo mugenda kuleetebwa mubalibwe tewali kintu kyonna kyemukola kigenda kwekweka
  69,19,Naye oyo alikwasibwa ekitabo kye mu mukono gwe ogwaddyo agenda kugamba nti abange mujje musome ekitabo kyange
  69,20,Mazima nali nkakasa nti ngenda kubalibwa
  69,21,Oyo nno agenda kubeera mu bulamu obwesiimisa
  69,22,Mu jjana ey'a waggulu
  69,23,Ebibala byayo nga birengejjera kumpi
  69,24,Kale mulye era munywe muyogeyoge olwebyo byemwakulembeza mu nnaku ezaayita
  69,25,Naye oyo alikwasibwa ekitabo kye mu mukono gwe ogwa kkono aligamba nti zinsanze singa siwereddwa kitabo kyange
  69,26,Era nessimanya kubalibwa kwange
  69,27,Waakiri singa bwennafa kyekyamala nessizuukira
  69,28,Ebyobugagga byange tebingasizza
  69,29,Sikyalina byakuwoza
  69,30,Mu kiseera ekyo Katonda agenda kulagira nti mumukwate mumulijje
  69,31,Bwemumala mumukasuke mu muliro
  69,32,Bwemumala mumuyiseemu olujegere oluwanvu bwalwo obwenkana emikono nsanvu
  69,33,Anti yali takkiriza Katonda owekitiibwa
  69,34,Era nga takubiriza kuliisa banaku
  69,35,N'olwekyo olwaleero wano talinawo muntu amulumirwa
  69,36,Nga bwatalina kyakulya okugyako masirasira
  69,37,Ebintu ebitayinza kulibwa okugyako abonoonyi
  69,38,Tewali kingana kulayira ebyo byemulaba
  69,39,Nebyo byemutalaba
  69,40,Mazima Kur'ani bigambo bya Katonda byeyassa ku mubaka (Nabbi Muhammad) ow'ekitiibwa
  69,41,Ssi bigambo bya mutontomi naye Iman yammwe yentono
  69,42,Era sibigambo bya mulaguzi naye mufumitiriza kitono (nemutasobola ku byawula)
  69,43,Byassibwa ku ye okuva eri omulezi w'ebitonde
  69,44,Singa yetantala natwogeza ebigambo byetutaamutuma
  69,45,Twalimukutteko n'amanyi
  69,46,Olwo nno netumukutula omusuwa gw'obulamu
  69,47,Era tewali mumwe ayinza kutulemesa kutuukiriza ekyo kuye
  69,48,Mazima yyo Kur'ani kyakwebuulirira eri abatya Katonda
  69,49,Era mazima ddala tumanyi nti mu mmwe mulimu abalimbisa (Kur'ani)
  69,50,Mazima okugirimbisa (Kur'ani) kugenda kubeera kwejjusa kunene eri abakafiiri
  69,51,Mazima yo Kur'ani ge mazima aga namaddala
  69,52,Kale nno tendereza erinnya lya Mukama Katonda wo owekitiibwa
  70,1,"Mu ngeri y'okunyomerera\" omu ku bakafiiri\" yasaba oba ebibonerezo bijja bijje, so nga ate ddala byakujja"
  70,2,Bituuke ku bakafiiri tewali agenda kubigaana kubatuukako
  70,3,Nga biva eri Katonda nnyini madaala agalinya muggulu
  70,4,"Ba Malayika nga ne Jiburilu mwomutwalidde mwebayita nga bolekera eri Katonda, ekibatwalira olunaku lumu lwokka naye nga ate lwenkanankana e myaka e mitwalo etaano (egy'okunsi)"
  70,5,Kale nno gumikiriza olugumikiriza olulungi
  70,6,Mazima bbo balaba ebibonerezo nga biri wala
  70,7,Ate nga ffe tulaba nga biri kumpi
  70,8,Ku lunaku eggulu lwelirikulukuta nga omuzigo omusanuuse
  70,9,Ate ensozi neziba nga pamba asunsuddwa
  70,10,Era tewali wamukwano agenda kubuuza bikwata ku ffa nfe we
  70,11,"Bagenda kuba nga beeraba (naye nga tebayinza kuyambagana). Omwonoonyi olwokwagala okuwona ebibonerezo byolunaku olwo, aliyagala okwenunula nga awaayo abaanabe"
  70,12,Mukyalawe ne mugandawe
  70,13,N'ekika kye ekimukuuma
  70,14,"Nabantu bonna abali munsi, nga ekyo akikola awone ebibonerezo bya Katonda"
  70,15,"Tekigenda kuba nga bwayagala, mazima ayolekedde muliro ogubumbujja"
  70,16,Ogusiriiriza ddala eddiba
  70,17,Gugenda kukowoola buli eyakubayo amabega nakyuka okuva ku mazima
  70,18,"Era nga yakungaanyanga emmali nagitereka \"natagyamu mugabo gugitukuza"
  70,19,Mazima omuntu yatondebwa nga wamulugube
  70,20,Nga bwatuukibwako akabi ayitirira okutya
  70,21,Ate bwaba afunye akalungi ayitirira obukodo
  70,22,Okugyako abo abayimirizaawo e sswala
  70,23,Abo nga okusaala kwabwe kwalubeerera
  70,24,Era abo mu by'obugagga byabwe mulimu omugabo ogumanyiddwa
  70,25,Guweebwa abasabi n'abafuna mpola
  70,26,Era bebo abakakasa o kubeerawo kw'olunaku lw'enkomerero
  70,27,Era abo abatya ebibonerezo bya Mukama Katonda waabwe
  70,28,Kubanga mazima ebibonerezo byamukama Katonda sibyakuwonwa
  70,29,Era abo abakuuma obwerere bwabwe
  70,30,"Okugyako ku bakyala babwe oba abazaana abali mu mikono gyabwe, anti bo tebanenyezebwa kwabo"
  70,31,"Omuntu asukka ku abo, abo nno be babuusi bensalo"
  70,32,"Era abantu abalungi abogeddwako waggulu, bebatuukiriza obwesigwa bwabwe nendagaano zaabwe"
  70,33,Era abo abeesimbu mu bujulizi bwabwe
  70,34,Era abo abasaala e sswala zaabwe mu bujjuvu
  70,35,Abo nno balibeera mu jjana nga baweebwa ebitiibwa
  70,36,"Lwaki abakafiiri bajja gyoli nga banguwa \"so nga ate bakulimbisa"
  70,37,Nga bali ku mukono gwo ogwa ddyo ne ku mukono ogwa kkono mu bibinja
  70,38,Buli omu kubo asuubira okuyingira e jjana eyebyengera
  70,39,"Nedda sibwekiri, mazima ffe twabakola nga tubajja mwebyo byebamanyi"
  70,40,"Ndayira Katonda nannyini buvanjuba nobugwanjuba, mazima ffe tusobolera ddala"
  70,41,Okubawanyisaamu abalungi ababasinga era tetuli ffe baakulemesebwa
  70,42,"Ggwe baveeko babeere mu bukafiiri bwabwe nga bwebazannya okutuusa lwebalisisinkana olunaku lwabwe, olwo lwebalaganyisibwa"
  70,43,Olunaku lwebalifuluma mu ntaana zaabwe nga baduma nga balinga abagenda eri ebendera ebatereddwawo
  70,44,"Amaaso gabwe makakkamu, obuswavu nga bubabuutikidde, olwo lwe lunaku lwe balaganyisibwa"
  71,1,Mazima ffe twatuma Nuhu eri abantu be. Nti tiisa abantubo nga ebibonerezo abiruma ennyo tebinabajjira
  71,2,Naabagamba nti mazima nze ndi mutiisa omunnyonnyozi
  71,3,Nti musinze Katonda era mu mutye nange mungondere
  71,4,Olwo nno ajja kubasonyiwa ebyonoono byammwe (bye mwakola nga temunnaba kukkiriza mubaka era alyoke abawonye okuzikirira n'ebibonerezo ebibamalawo olumu). Abalindirize abatuuse ku ntuuko ze yabagerera. Mazima entuuko za Katonda bweziba zituuse tezirindirizibwa singa muba mumanyi
  71,5,"Awamu nekyo tebakkiriza\", Nuhu naagamba nti ayi Katonda wange nkowodde abantu bange ekiro n'emisana"
  71,6,Wabula okukowoola kwange tekubongedde okugyako okunnesamba
  71,7,"Mazima buli lwembadde mbakowoola badde eri okusonyiwa kwo bassa ennwe zaabwe mu matu gaabwe, ne beebikka engoye zaabwe, ne bakalambira era ne beekuluntaza olw'ekuluntaza"
  71,8,Ate era mazima mbakowodde mulwatu
  71,9,Era njogedde nabo mu lujjudde nga bwenjogedde nabo kinnomu
  71,10,Nembagamba nti mwegayirire Katonda wa mmwe anti mazima yye bulijjo musonyiyi
  71,11,Olwonno ajja kubatonnyeseza enkuba ey'omuddiringanwa
  71,12,Era abawe mu bungi emmaali n'abaana abawe n'amasamba abateeremu n'emigga
  71,13,Naye lwaki Katonda temumuwa kitiibwa
  71,14,Sso nga yabatonda ngabayisa mumitendera egyenjawulo
  71,15,Abaffe temulaba engeri Katondawo gyeyakolamu eggulu omusanvu nga myaliiro
  71,16,Nassaamu omwezi nga kitangaala nga bweyassamu enjuba nga eyaka
  71,17,Katonda yabatandika ng'abajja muttaka nemujja nga mukula nga ebimera bwe bikula
  71,18,Oluvanyuma abazza mu ttaka nga era bwagenda okubazuukiza alibagyemu bulambalamba (nga temuyise mu mitendera nga ebimera)
  71,19,Era Katonda yabateerawo ensi nga esoboka okuwangalirwako
  71,20,Mube nga musobola okutambulira muyo nga mukwata amakubo ge muba mwagadde
  71,21,"Nuhu kwekugamba nti, ayi mukama wange mazima ddala abantu abo banjemedde nebasalawo okugoberera oyo yenna emmaali ye n'abaana be bebitayongera okugyako okufafaganirwa"
  71,22,Nebakola olukwe sinziggu (bwebagezaako okutta Nuhu)
  71,23,Era nebagamba nti temugeza nemuva ku ba Katonda ba mmwe naddala Wadda ne Suwa'a ne Yagutha ne Yauka ne Nasira
  71,24,Olwekyo baabuza abantu bangi (Nange kyenva nkusaba nti) mukama Katonda abantu abeyisa obubi tobongera okugyako kubula
  71,25,Olwobwonoonyi bwabwe baazikiziribwa nebayingizibwa omuliro baali tebayinza kufuna abataasa yenna
  71,26,"Ye Nuhu kwekugamba nti, ayi Katonda wange toleka kunsi mukafiiri yenna"
  71,27,Anti singa obalekawo bajja kubuza abaddu bo era buli gwebanazaala ajja kuba mwononefu omukafiiri
  71,28,"Ayi Mukama Katonda wange nsonyiwa ne bakadde bange na buli yenna anaayingira mu nju yange kavuna anaaba nga mukkiriza, era nkusaba osonyiwe abakkiriza abasajja n'abakkiriza abakazi, wabula bo abeeyisa obubi tobongera okugyako okuzikirira"
  72,1,Bagambe ggwe Nabbi Muhammad nti nafuna obubaka nga waliwo amajinni agamu agaawuliriza nga nsoma Kur'ani negagamba nti mazima Kur'ani tugiwulidde nga yewuunyisa
  72,2,"Ekowoola oyo agiwuliriza okudda eri obulungamu era naffe tugikkirizza, era tetugenda kuddayo kugatta ku Katonda kintu kirala"
  72,3,"Era mazima ekitiibwa kya Mukama Katonda waffe kisukkulumu, tayinza kuba nti yeteerawo mukyala wadde omwana"
  72,4,Era mazima ddala ababuyabuya muffe baayogera nga ku Katonda ebigambo ebitemerere
  72,5,Era mazima ddala ffe twalowoozanga nti abantu na majjini baali tebayinza kwogera ku Katonda byabulimba
  72,6,Waliwo abantu abamu abaasabanga obuyambi okuva eri amajinni ekyagongera okuwaganyala
  72,7,Era mazima ddala amajinni gaalowooza nga bwemwalowooza nti Katonda yali tagenda kutuma mubaka yenna
  72,8,Era mazima ffe tubadde tugezaako okugenda ku ggulu netulisanga nga lijjudde abakuumi abakambwe nebitawuliro
  72,9,"Era mazima ffe waliwo enfo zetwatulangamu netuwuliriza ebifaayo, naye kati agezaako okuwuliriza asanga ebitawuliro nga bimuteeze"
  72,10,Wabula tetumanyi mu kukola ekyo kwali kulumya bitonde ebiri ku nsi oba Mukama Katonda wabyo yabyagaliza bulungamu
  72,11,Mazima nemuffe mulimu abalongoofu n'abatali era tuli ebibiina ebyenjawulo
  72,12,Era ffe tuli bakakafu nti tetuyinza kulemesa Katonda ku nsi era nga bwetutayinza kumulemesa ne tumuddukako
  72,13,"Era mazima ddala bwe twawulira obulungamu twabukkiriza, nga ate oyo yenna akkiriza Mukama Katonda we tayinza kutya butasasulwa oba okunyigirizibwa"
  72,14,"Mazima ddala muffe mulimu abasiramu nga bwemulimu abaabula. Oyo yenna asiramuka, abo nno bebaba banoonya amazima mu bwegendereza"
  72,15,Wabula bo abaabula be bagenda okubeera enku z'omuliro Jahannama
  72,16,Naye singa abantu banywerera ku kkubo ettuufu twalibawadde enkuba mu bungi
  72,17,"Tulyoke tubageseze ngeri ki gye be bazaamu e byengera, oyo yenna eyeesamba ebigambo bya Katondawe agenda kumubonereza n'ebibonerezo ebikambwe"
  72,18,"Mazima ddala emizigiti gya kusinzizamu Katonda yekka, kale nno temugatta ku Katonda ekintu kyonna"
  72,19,Era mazima ddala omuddu w'a Katonda (Nabbi Muhammad) bweyayimirira nga asaala amajinni gaasembera negamwetoloola kumpi kumwetuumako nga gali mu bibinja
  72,20,Bagambe (Gwe Nabbi Muhammad) nti mazima nze nsinza Katonda wange ate si mugattako kintu kirala kyonna
  72,21,(Ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) bagambe nti tekiri mu mikono gyange okubaggyirawo obuzibu obuba bubatuuseeko nga bwe kitali mu busobozi bwange okubafunira obulungamu
  72,22,Era bagambe nti mazima nze tewali muntu yenna ayinza kumponya bibonerezo bya Katonda singa mba mujeemedde. Era sisobola kufuna buddukiro nga si bwa Katonda
  72,23,"Nekiba nga ekisigadde kubatuusako bubaka obuva eri Katonda, naye abo bonna abajeemera Katonda n'omubakawe baakuyingira omuliro Jahannama, era nga b'akugubeeramu olubeerera"
  72,24,Okutuusizza ddala bwe balibanga balabye ebyo ebyabalagaanyisibwa olwo nno lwe bajja okukakasa nti ani alina omutaasa omunafu neggye ettono
  72,25,Bagambe ggwe Nabbi Muhammad nti mazima nze simanyi oba e bibonerezo bye mulaganyisibwa biri kumpi oba byakujja oluvanyuma lwebbanga eggwanvu
  72,26,"Ye yekka, Katonda yaamanyi ebitamanyiddwa ng'ate talina yenna gwabikkulira e byamabye"
  72,27,"Okugyako oyo gwaba alonze okubeera omubaka (kale nno oyo amubikkulira ebimu ku byamabye) era amuteerawo obukuumi bwa Malayika nga bamwetolodde, Sitani obutasobola kumutuukako"
  72,28,Nabbi alyoke amanye nti mazima ba Nabbi baatuukiriza obubaka bwa Katonda waabwe (nga naye bwa butuukiriza) era bamanye nti Katonda amanyi ebyo byonna bye bakola nga era bwamanyi buli kintu kyonna
  73,1,Owange ggwe eyeebikkirira (olwokutya okwakutuukako bwewafuna obubaka okuva ku Malayika Jiburilu omulundi ogwasoka)
  73,2,Golokoka osaale ekiro mpozzi lekayo akaseera katono
  73,3,Oyinza okusaala ekitundu kye kiro oba okukendezaako katono
  73,4,Oba oyinza okwongerako era bwoba osoma Kur'ani giwoomese
  73,5,Mazima ffe tujja kukutikka e kigambo ekizito
  73,6,Anti e sswala enzuukukire y'esinga okubuulirira omuntu (olw'okwerekereza otulo) era nga nebisomerwamu byebisinga okusomwa munsoma ennambulukufu
  73,7,Anti obudde obwemisana oleebukana nnyo (mu bintu ebirala)
  73,8,"Kale nno tendereza erinnya lya Mukama Katondawo, e kiseera kyonna okimuwe"
  73,9,"Mukama Katonda omufuziwo buvanjuba n'obugwanjuba tewali kirala kyonna kisaanye kusinzibwa okugyako yye, kale nno gwoba wesigamako"
  73,10,Era ogumikirize kw'ebyo bye boogera era obaveeko mu ngeri e nnungi
  73,11,"Naye ndekera abalimbisa, abagagga fugge, era balindirize akaseera katono"
  73,12,Mazima tulina empingu n'omuliro Jahiim
  73,13,N'ebyokulya ebitamirika n'ebibonerezo ebiruma
  73,14,Ebiribaawo ku lunaku e nsi n'ensozi lw'ebirikankana e nsozi ne zifuuka entuumo z'omusenyu ogufuumuka
  73,15,(Okuwona ebyo mukozese omukisa gwokuba nti) mazima ffe twabatumira omubaka nga yajja okubawaako obujulizi okufaananako nga bwe twatumira Firawo omubaka
  73,16,"Wabula Firawo yajeemera omubaka, kyetwava tumukwata olukwata olwamanyi"
  73,17,Kakati bwe mujeema muliwona mutya olunaku olulifuula abaana abato abakadde
  73,18,"Ate nga eggulu ligenda kuyulikamu olwebiribaawo ku lunaku olwo, nga ate Katonda kyalagaanyisa kiteekwa okutuukirira"
  73,19,"(Bwekiba nga bwekityo bwekiri), mazima ddala muteekwa mutwale Kur'ani nga kyakwebuulirira. N'olwekyo ayagala okuwona ateekeddwa okukwata ekkubo erimuzza eri Katonda we"
  73,20,"Mazima Katonda wo akimanyi nti oyimirira ekiro ng'osaala emirundi egimu kumpi bibiri byakusatu byekiro, oluusi kimu kyakubiri nga n'olundi kimu kyakusatu era nga naabamu ku bakkiriza abali naawe bwebatyo bwe bakola nga ate Katonda yaawa ebiragiro ebikola ekiro n'emisana, era nga amanyi nti temuyinza kumalayo kiro kyonna nga mukola Ibaada kye yava abawa ekisonyiwo, kale nno musome kyemuba musobodde mu Kur'ani nga musaala ekiro anti amanyi nti mu mmwe mulimu abalwadde nga n'abalala bagenda kubeera mu safari nga batambudde mu nsi olwokunoonya ebigabwa bya Katonda nga nabandi bagenda kubeera mu ntabaalo z'okuweereza mu kkubo lya Katonda n'olwekyo musome ekyo kye muba musobodde mu Kur'ani nga musaala e sswala ya tahajjudi era muyimirizeewo e sswala eza faradha mutoole ne zzaka mu ngeri y'emu muwole Katonda oluwola olulungi nga muwaayo saddaaka. Akalungi konna kemweterekera mugenda ku kasanga mu maaso ga Katonda. Okukola ekyo kirungi era kyekirimu empeera ennene era musabe Katonda ekisonyiwo mazima Katonda musonyiyi oweekisa"
  74,1,Owange ggwe eyeebikiridde (olwokutya Malayika Jiburilu lwe yakuleetera obubaka okuva eri Katonda)
  74,2,Golokoka otiise abantu ebibonerezo bya Katonda
  74,3,Ne Mukama Katondawo yekka gwoba ogulumiza
  74,4,N'engoyezo zitukuze
  74,5,Amasanamu geewalire ddala
  74,6,Tokoleranga abantu obulungi ng'ogenderera kufunamu bulungi kuno ku nsi
  74,7,Beeranga mugumikiriza osobole okufuna okusiima kwa Mukama Katondawo
  74,8,Engombe bwerifuuyibwa (kulwokuzuukira)
  74,9,Olunaku olwo lugenda kuba lunaku luzito
  74,10,Terugenda kuba lwangu eri abakafiiri
  74,11,(Owange ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) ndeka nooyo gwe nnetondera
  74,12,Nemuwa ebyobugagga ebiyitirivu
  74,13,Nemuwa nabaana abatutumufu
  74,14,Ne mugaziyiriza olugaziya (e byenfuna obukulembeze n'ekitiibwa)
  74,15,Oluvanyuma alulunkanira okumwongera okusingako awo
  74,16,Nedda sijja kumwongera kuba yawakanya ebigambo byaffe (Kur'ani)
  74,17,Nja kumussaako e bibonerezo e bizito
  74,18,Anti mazima yye (Al Walid bin Mugiira) yalowooza era naasalawo okuvvoola Kur'ani
  74,19,Nakolimirwa okusinziira ku ngeri gyeyasalawo
  74,20,Era ddala yakolimirwa ku ngeri gyeyasalawo
  74,21,Oluvanyuma yakirowozaako
  74,22,Olwo nno ne yeekaba najja emitaafu
  74,23,Ne kyaddirira ebituufu yabivaako neyekuluntaza
  74,24,Olwo nno n'alangirira nti e bigambo bya Muhammad temuli wabula ddogo erijjibwa ku balogo abasooka
  74,25,Era byayogera tebisukka ku kuba bigambo bya muntu
  74,26,"(Katonda naagamba nti:) nja kumuyingiza omuliro Sakara"
  74,27,Naye omanyi Sakara kyeki
  74,28,Gwo muliro ogutagenda kulekawo kintu wadde okukitaliza
  74,29,Gwokera ddala negusiriiza eddiba lyomuntu
  74,30,Gukuumibwa ba Malayika kkumi na mwenda
  74,31,"Ate omulimu gwokukuuma omuliro tetwaguwa okugyako ba Malayika, era omuwendo gwabwe tetwaguteekawo okugyako nga kikemo eri abatakkiriza Katonda, so nga abo abaweebwa ekitabo ekyo kibongera kukakasa (ebyo bye baalina), ate bo abakkiriza (abagoberezi ba Nabbi Muhammad) kyongera kunyweza bukkiriza bwabwe, era abaweebwa ekitabo n'abakkiriza babe nga tebasigalamu kakunkuna, wabula nga (abanafunsi) abalina obulwadde mu mitima gyabwe n'abatakkiriza bagamba nti Katonda kiki kyagenderera mu kifananyi kino, bwatyo nno Katonda abuza nalungamya oyo gwaba ayagadde, ate tewali amanyi ggye lya Mukama Katondawo okugyako yye, ebyo byonna ebyogeddwa tewali kibigendererwamu okugyako okubuulirira omuntu"
  74,32,"Nedda (tekiri ng'abantu abamu bwe balowooza), mazima ndayidde omwezi"
  74,33,Ne ndayira n'ekiro mu kiseera we kiggwerako
  74,34,Ne ndayira n'amakya ngabusasaana
  74,35,Mazima ggwo (omuliro Sakara) kye kimu ku binene
  74,36,Ebyandibadde bibuulirira omuntu
  74,37,Eri oyo aba ayagadde mu mmwe okudda eri Katondawe oba okumwesamba
  74,38,Buli muntu agenda kubeera musingo gwa mirimugye
  74,39,Okugyako abo abalibeera ku mukono ogwaddyo
  74,40,Bagenda kubeera mu jjana nga babuuza ebifa
  74,41,Ku bonoonyi
  74,42,Nga babagamba nti ki ekibayingizza omuliro
  74,43,Baligamba nti tetubangako mu basaaze
  74,44,Era tetwaliisanga banaku
  74,45,Twabeeranga nabakubi bambekuulo
  74,46,Era twali tulimbisa olunaku lw'enkomerero
  74,47,Okutuusa okufa lw'ekwatutuukako
  74,48,Kale tebagenda kuganyulwa mu kuwolereza kwa bawolereza
  74,49,Kakano kiki ekibaddusa okuva ku kubuulirira kwa (Kur'ani kuno)
  74,50,Nga balinga entulege ezigobeddwa
  74,51,Ezidduka e mpologoma
  74,52,Wabula buli omu mubo ayagala aweebwe ebiwandiiko ebibikuddwa
  74,53,Nedda ekituufu kiri nti bbo tebakkiriza nkomerero
  74,54,Mazima ddala yo (Kur'ani) kyakubuulirira
  74,55,Oyo aba ayagadde yeebulirira nayo
  74,56,"Wabula tebayinza kwebuulirira okugyako nga Katonda ayagadde, yye ye nanyini kutiibwa era ye nanyini kusonyiwa"
  75,1,Tewali kingaana kulayira lunaku lwakuzuukira
  75,2,Era nga bwewatali kingaana kulayira omwoyo ogwejjusa
  75,3,Abaffe omuntu alowooza nti tetugenda kusobola kuzzaawo magumbage
  75,4,Nedda tukisobolera ddala nga bwetulisobola okuzzaawo ennwe zaabwe
  75,5,Wabula omuntu emirundi egisinga ayagala nnyo okuwangaalira mu kwonoona
  75,6,Ngabuuza (mu ngeri ey'okujerega n'okuwakanya) nti olunaku lwokuzuukira lulibaawo ddi
  75,7,Ddala lugenga kubaawo nga n'amaaso g'abantu galiralambala olwokutya
  75,8,Ekitangala kyomwezi kigenda kuggwawo
  75,9,Enjuba n'omwezi birigattibwa (nga tewakyasobola kubaawo kiro namisana)
  75,10,Ku lunaku olwo omuntu agenda kwebuuza nti nzirukirewa
  75,11,"Kyekyo ddala, tewagenda kubaawo muntu weyekweka"
  75,12,Obuddo ku lunaku olwo bujja kuba eri Mukama Katondawo
  75,13,Ku lunaku olwo omuntu agenda kutegeezebwa ebyo byonna byeyakola nebyataakola
  75,14,Wabula ate ddala omuntu ye yennyini amanyi bye yakola ne byataakola (newakubadde nga aligezaako okwogera kino nakiri ngayeetonda)
  75,15,Newakubadde nga aligezaako okwogera kino nakiri ngayetonda
  75,16,Bwoba osoma Kur'ani toyanguyiriza nga olowooza nti kyekinakuyamba okuginyweeza
  75,17,Anti okugikungaanya kuli kuffe nga era bwekiri kuffe okunywereza ku lulimi lwo ensoma ennungi
  75,18,Kale nno bwetumala okugikusomera (nga tugiyisa ku Jiburilu) goberera ensoma yaayo
  75,19,Era mazima okuginnyonnyola kuli kuffe
  75,20,(Ebyo ebyogeddwa waggulu bimala omuntu okwebuulirira nabyo) wabula ebyembi mmwe mwagala ebyokufuna byensi ebyamangu
  75,21,Nemuleka ebyolunaku lw’enkomerero
  75,22,Ebyenyi bya bantu abamu ku lunaku olwo bigenda kuba nga bitemagana
  75,23,Bigenda kutunula ku Mukama Katonda waabyo
  75,24,Ate nga ebyenyi bya bantu abalala bigenda kuba binyikaavu
  75,25,Nga bimanyidde ddala nti bigenda kutuukibwako akabi akanene akamenya nenkizi
  75,26,Naye omwoyo bwegutuuka mu ddokooli
  75,27,Abantu webagambira nti ani alina eddagala eriyinza okumuwonya
  75,28,Wabula yye ngamaze okukakasa nti agenda kufa
  75,29,Entumbwe ne yeegatta ku ntumbwe
  75,30,Olwo nno obuddo buba busigadde eri Katondawo
  75,31,Naye nga omufu teyasaddaaka wadde okusaala
  75,32,Wabula yalimbisa ebigambo bya Katonda nabyesamba
  75,33,Olwo nno naatambula nadda eri abantu be nga yeeraga
  75,34,(Aligambibwa nti ekyo) ekikutuuseeko kikugwanidde era ddala kikugwanidde (owange ggwe omwonoonyi)
  75,35,Ate era kikugwanidde ng'ate era ddala kikugwanidde
  75,36,Omuntu alowooza nti ayinza okulekwa neyeeyisa nga bwayagala
  75,37,Tajjukira nti yasooka kuba tondo lyamazzi agazaala agateekebwa mu nabaana
  75,38,"Oluvanyuma naafuuka ekisayisayi, olwo Katonda naamutonda namussaako byonna ebimufuula omuntu"
  75,39,"Nga bwatyo bwakola emitendera ebiri, omusajja n'omukazi"
  75,40,Abaffe oyo eyakola omuntu mu ngeri eyo tasobola kulamusa bafu
  76,1,Omuntu tajjukira nti waayitawo ekiseera kinene nga tayogerwako (nga tannatondebwa)
  76,2,Mazima ffe twatonda omuntu nga ava mu kwetabula kwamazzi (ag'omusajja n'omukazi) naye nga waakugezesebwa mu bulamu bwe. Kyetwava tumuwa okuwulira n'okulaba
  76,3,"Mazima ddala twamulaga e kkubo, kiri gyali yeebaza naasinza Katonda omu oba ajeema n'awakanya"
  76,4,Mazima ddala abakafiiri twabategekera enjegere n'amakoligo n'omuliro ogutuntumuka
  76,5,Mazima abakozi bobulungi bagenda kunywa ekyokunywa nga kitabuddwa mu kafuura
  76,6,"Olwo nno luliba luzzi abaddu b'a Katonda abeeyisa obulungi kwebagendanga okunywa, lugenda kukulukuta nga buli muntu lumutuukako waali"
  76,7,"(Bagenda kutuuka kwebyo kubanga) kuno ku nsi baatuukiriza nnaziri zaabwe, era nga batya olunaku olwo obuzibu bwalwo obugenda okubuutikira e nsi n'eggulu"
  76,8,Era bagabira abanaku ne bamulekwa nabasibe emmere awamu n'okuba nti bo bennyini bagyetaaga
  76,9,Nga bagamba nti mazima tubaliisa lwa Katonda tetubaagalamu mpeera wadde okwebaza
  76,10,(Ekitukozesa bino lwakuba nti) mazima ddala ffe tutya engeri gye tulisisinkanamu Katonda waffe ku lunaku e byenyi (bya bantu) lwe birijjula emitaafu nga byekabye
  76,11,N'olwekyo nno Katonda wakubawonya obuzibu bw'olunaku olwo era abawe okutangalijja kwe byenyi awamu n'essanyu
  76,12,"Era wakubasasula olwobugumikiriza, nga abayingiza e jjana omuli ebyambalo bya Siliki (awamu nokuba nti kunsi abasajja baaziyizibwa okumwambala)"
  76,13,"Balituula mu ntebe ez'omuwendo nga besigamye, tebagenda kutukwako kwokya kwanjuba wadde obutiti"
  76,14,"Era nga mulimu emiti egiribakolera ebisiikirize, era nga nebibala byamu bigenda kuba byangu byakunoga"
  76,15,Baligabulirwa ku sowane eza feeza era bakunywera ku girasi ezitemagana
  76,16,"Ziritemegana anti ziriba zaakolebwa mu feeza, ziriba zimala bumazi okubeeramu ekyokunywa ekimalawo obwetaavu bwoyo anywa"
  76,17,Era bagenda kuweebwa eby'okunywa ebiri mu girasi nga bitabulwamu entangawuzi
  76,18,"Eyo nno egenda kuba nsulo mu jjana eyitibwa \"Salsabiila"
  76,19,"Bagenda kuweerezebwanga abaweereza abolubeerera, nga bwobatunulako bwoti olaba lu'ulu asasanyiziddwa"
  76,20,Buli wonotunulanga mu jjana ng'olaba ebyengera ebisuffu n'obwanannyini obutaliiko kkomo
  76,21,"Baliba bambadde engoye eza Siliki omuweweevu owakiragala ne Siliki omuzito, era bagenda kuba bawundiddwa nebikomo ebya feeza, era Mukama Katonda waabwe agenda kubawa ebyokunywa ebitukuvu"
  76,22,"(Baligambwa nti) Mazima ebyo byonna yempeera yammwe, mazima okutegana kwa mmwe kusiimiddwa"
  76,23,Mazima ffe twakussaako Kur'ani (gwe Nabbi Muhammad) olussa
  76,24,"Kale nno beera mugumikiriza ku kugera kwa Katondawo, togezaako okugondera omwonoonyi oba omuwakanyi yenna"
  76,25,Era yogeranga kulinnya lya Mukama Katondawo enkya neggulo
  76,26,Ne mukiro muvunnamire ng'osaala era omutendereze mu ttumbi ebbanga ggwanvu
  76,27,"Mazima abatakkiriza basinga kwagala birungi byansi ebyamangu, ne basuulayo gwannaggamba ku bikwata ku lunaku lw'enkomerero oluzito"
  76,28,"Ffe twabatonda ne tugumya e biyungo byabwe, naye nga bwe tuba twagadde (tuyinza okubazikiriza) ne tuleeta abantu abalala"
  76,29,"Mazima obubaka bwa Kur'ani buno kya kwebulirira era nga kyakujjukiza, n'olwekyo aba ayagadde asanye y'eteerewo ekkubo erimutuusa eri Katondawe"
  76,30,"Naye ate temusobola kwagala okugyako nga Katonda ayagadde, mazima Katonda lubeerera amanyi, assa buli kintu mussa lyako"
  76,31,"Ayingiza oyo gwaba ayagadde mu kusaasirakwe, ate bbo abalyazamanyi yabategekera ebibonerezo ebiruma"
  77,1,Ndayidde empewo ekunta mu ngeri y'okugoberegana
  77,2,Era ndayidde kibuyaga akunta mu ngeri ey'amaanyi eyakabi
  77,3,Era ndayidde Malayika ezitambuza ebire olutambuza (olwokutonyesa enkuba)
  77,4,Era ndayidde Malayika ezikka okuva ewa Katonda nga zireeta ebyawula wakati w'amazima n'obulimba
  77,5,Era ndayidde Malayika ezireeta ebitabo n'obubaka eri ba Nabbi ba Katonda nga byakujjukiza
  77,6,Mu ngeri yokuba nti bijjawo ebyokwekwaasa oba nga byakutiisa
  77,7,Mazima bye mulaganyisibwa ebikwata ku lunaku lw'enkomerero n'okusasulwa bya kubaawo
  77,8,Emunyeenye lweziriggibwawo (newataba kitangaala kyaazo)
  77,9,Era eggulu bweririwumulwa (nerirabika nga emiryango)
  77,10,Era ensozi bwezirimerengulwa
  77,11,Era ababaka b'a Katonda bwebaliweebwa akadde k'okuwa obujulizi kwabo bebaatumwamu
  77,12,(Ebintu ebyo ebyentiisa) biribaawo ddi
  77,13,Bigenda kubaawo ku lunaku olwokusalawo n'okulamula wakati w'ebitonde
  77,14,Abaffe omanyi olunaku lw'okusalawo kyekki
  77,15,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kw'abo abalulimbisa
  77,16,Abaffe tetwazikiriza ababasokawo
  77,17,Netubagoberezaako abalala
  77,18,Bwetutyo nno bwetukola mu kubonereza abonoonyi
  77,19,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,20,Abaffe tetwabakola nga tubajja mu mazzi aganyomebwa
  77,21,Netugateeka mukifo ekigakuuma
  77,22,Okutuusa ebbanga eggere erimanyiddwa
  77,23,Bwetutyo nno bwetwateekateeka okutondebwa kwabwe tuli bateesiteesi abasinga obulungi
  77,24,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,25,Abaffe ensi tetwagikola nga ekungaanya
  77,26,Abalamu n'abafu (bonna ngabali muyo)
  77,27,Netugiteekamu e nsozi eziginyweza entumbiivu ne tubawa amazzi amalungi
  77,28,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,29,Ku lunaku lw'enkomerero abakafiiri baliragirwa nti mugende eri ebyo bye mwali mulimbisa
  77,30,Mugende eri ekisiikirize ekyomuliro ngakirimu ebitundu bisatu
  77,31,Wabula tebaliba na kibasiikiriza wadde e kibataasa nnimi z'amuliro
  77,32,Mazima omuliro ogwo gukasuka ebitawuliro nga biringa ebizimbe ebigulumivu
  77,33,Ebitawuliro ebyo nga biringa engamiya ez'akyenvu
  77,34,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,35,Olwo lunaku lwebatagenda kwogera
  77,36,Wadde okukkirizibwa okwetonda
  77,37,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,38,Luno lwe lunaku lw'okulamula tubakunganyizza mwenna n'aba bakulembera
  77,39,Bwe muba mulina engeri gyemuyinza okwebulankanyamu kale munnebulankanyeko
  77,40,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,41,Naye mazima abatya Katonda bagenda kubeera mu bisiikirize n'emigga egikulukuta
  77,42,N'ebibala byebaliba bagala
  77,43,Nga bagambibwa nti mulye era munywe nga mweyagala
  77,44,Mazima ffe bwetutyo bwetusasula abakozi b'obulungi
  77,45,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,46,"(Kuno ku nsi abakafiiri bagambwa nti) mulye, era mweyagale kitono, wabula mumanye nti muli bonoonyi (naye mukimanye nti waliyo enkomerero)"
  77,47,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,48,Bwebalagirwa okusaala tebasaala
  77,49,Ku lunaku olwo okubonaabona kugenda kubeera kwabo abalulimbisa
  77,50,Olwo bigamboki ebitali Kur'ani byebagenda okukkiriza